ENDPOINTS - BACKEND HV LOGYSER
CONFIGURATION ENDPOINTS
1. Get Identification Types
Method: GET

URL: /api/config/tipo-identificacion

Description: Get available identification types

2. Get Departments
Method: GET

URL: /api/config/departamentos

Description: Get all Colombian departments

3. Get Cities by Department
Method: GET

URL: /api/config/ciudades?departamento={department}

Parameters: department (required)

Description: Get cities for a specific department

4. Get EPS
Method: GET

URL: /api/config/eps

Description: Get available EPS

5. Get Pension Funds
Method: GET

URL: /api/config/pension

Description: Get available pension funds

APPLICANT ENDPOINTS
6. Get Applicant by ID
Method: GET

URL: /api/aspirante?identificacion={id}

Parameters: identificacion (required)

Description: Check if applicant exists and get all data

7. Upload Profile Photo
Method: POST

URL: /api/hv/upload-photo

Content-Type: multipart/form-data

Body: identificacion (string), photo (file - max 5MB)

Description: Upload photo to Google Cloud Storage

8. Complete CV Registration
Method: POST

URL: /api/hv/registrar

Content-Type: application/json

Description: Register or update complete applicant data including personal info, education, work experience, family, references, emergency contact, goals, and security questionnaire

EMAIL ENDPOINTS
9. Email Routes
Base URL: /api/correo

Description: Email-related routes (defined in separate module)

SERVER CONFIGURATION
Port: 8080 (configurable via PORT environment variable)

Database: MySQL on port 3307

Storage: Google Cloud Storage (bucket: hojas_vida_logyser)

CORS: Enabled for all origins

IMPORTANT NOTES
No authentication required in this version

File upload limit: 5MB for photos

PDF is automatically generated after successful registration

Existing applicants are updated with new data